## Logistic Regression


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Fit logistic regression to predict event occurrence
logistic_model <- glm(event_occurred ~ age + sex + treatment_group, data = clinical_trial_data, family = binomial)
summary(logistic_model)
```

